app.post() (Create Data)
📌 Use

👉 Server par data bhejne ke liye

💻 Example
app.use(express.json());

app.post('/user', (req, res) => {
    const data = req.body;
    res.send("User Created: " + data.name);
});
🔍 Explanation
express.json() → body parse karta hai
req.body → client se aaya data
POST → new data create
